[line]

[size=5]🎮 How Effects Work[/size]

Each interaction has a [b]type[/b] that determines what happens to the target crop:

[code]
Effect Type         | ✅ Positive                                            | ❌ Negative
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
⚡ Growth Speed     | Advances growth phase                                 | Delays day progress in current phase
⭐ Quality          | Applies/upgrades fertilizer (Basic → Quality → Deluxe)| Downgrades/removes fertilizer
📦 Quantity         | Advances growth (more harvest cycles)                 | Resets day progress (fewer harvests)
💧 Default          | Auto-waters dry soil                                  | Dries out watered soil
[/code]

Effects are processed [b]once at the start of each day[/b] and [b]every 2 in-game hours[/b]. Each effect has a random chance to trigger based on the interaction's strength multiplied by your configured Effect Strength.

[line]

[size=5]⚙️ Configuration[/size]

All options can be changed via [b]Generic Mod Config Menu[/b] or by editing [font=Courier New]config.json[/font]:

[code]
Option                | Default  | Description
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
EnableMod             | true     | Enable or disable the mod
EffectStrength        | 0.5      | Global multiplier for all effects (0.0 – 1.0)
ShowEffectMessages    | true     | Show in-game messages when interactions occur
ShowParticleEffects   | true     | Show sparkle particles on affected crops
ShowHoverText         | true     | Show tooltip when hovering over affected crops
[/code]

[line]

[size=5]📥 Installation[/size]

[list=1]
[*]Install [url=https://smapi.io/]SMAPI[/url] (4.0+)
[*][i](Optional)[/i] Install [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/5098]Generic Mod Config Menu[/url] for in-game configuration
[*]Download this mod and unzip it into your [font=Courier New]Stardew Valley/Mods[/font] folder
[*]Launch the game through SMAPI
[/list]

