[line]

[size=5]💡 Tips for Players[/size]

[list]
[*]🫘 [b]Green Beans are your best friend[/b] — They fix nitrogen and benefit ALL nearby crops. Plant them everywhere!
[*]🌻 [b]Sunflowers and Fairy Roses are area buffers[/b] — They help all crops in a 2-tile radius
[*]🍓 [b]Don't mass-plant strawberries[/b] — They compete with each other when too close
[*]🎃 [b]Isolate your pumpkins[/b] — They drain nutrients from everything nearby
[*]💠 [b]Give Sweet Gem Berries space[/b] — Any crop next to them causes negative effects
[*]☕ [b]Coffee is a great neighbor[/b] — Stimulates growth in all nearby plants
[*]🧄🍓 [b]Garlic + Strawberry[/b] is one of the strongest positive combos in spring
[/list]

